<div class="pt-2 mt-5 col-12">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-6">
        <h2>Set your emergency contact</h2>
        <p>Assign a person who will receive your trip details in the event at a preset date and time if you donâ€™t report back as safe by the end of your hike.</p>
